er}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Hermann Baumann (wrestler)|Hermann Baumann]]|SUI|1948 Summer}}\n|-\n|[[Wrestling at the 1952 Summer Olympics|1952 Helsinki]]<br>{{DetailsLink|Wrestling at the 1952 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle lightweight}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Olle Anderberg]]|SWE|1952 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Jay Thomas Evans]]|USA|1952 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Jahanbakht Towfigh]]|IRI|1952 Summer}}\n|-\n|[[Wrestling at the 1956 Summer Olympics|1956 Melbourne]]<br>{{DetailsLink|Wrestling at the 1956 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle lightweight}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Emam-Ali Habibi]]|IRI|1956 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Shigeru Kasahara]]|JPN|1956 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Alimbeg Bestayev]]|URS|1956 Summer}}\n|-\n|[[Wrestling at the 1960 Summer Olympics|1960 Rome]]<br>{{DetailsLink|Wrestling at the 1960 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle lightweight}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Shelby Wilson]]|USA|1960 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Vladimir Synyavsky]]|URS|1960 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Enyu Valchev]]|BUL|1960 Summer}}\n|-\n|[[Wrestling at the 1964 Summer Olympics|1964 Tokyo]]<br>{{DetailsLink|Wrestling at the 1964 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle lightweight}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Enyu Valchev]]|BUL|1964 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Klaus Rost]]|EUA|1964 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Iwao Horiuchi]]|JPN|1964 Summer}}\n|-\n|[[Wrestling at the 1968 Summer Olympics|1968 Mexico City]]<br>{{DetailsLink|Wrestling at the 1968 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle lightweight}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Abdollah Movahed]]|IRI|1968 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Enyu Valchev]]|BUL|1968 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Danzandarjaagiin Sereeter]]|MGL|1968 Summer}}\n|-\n|[[Wrestling at the 1972 Summer Olympics|1972 Munich]]<br>{{DetailsLink|Wrestling at the 1972 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle 68 kg}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Dan Gable]]|USA|1972 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Kikuo Wada]]|JPN|1972 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Ruslan Ashuraliyev