oland|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Mexico|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|East Germany|1959|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Chile|size=22px}} (until 1973)\n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| {{flagicon|Nicaragua|size=22px}} [[Somoza family|Somoza Dynasty]]<br/>{{flag|United States|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Israel|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Saudi Arabia|1938|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Honduras|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Chile|size=22px}} (since 1973)<br/>{{flag|Brazil|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Paraguay|1954|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Argentina|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Panama|size=22px}}<br/>{{flagicon|Germany|size=22px}} [[West Germany]]<br/>{{flag|Pakistan|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Philippines|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Iran|size=22px}} (indirectly)\n|style=\"background:#D0FFD0\"| '''Victory: Regime change in Nicaragua'''\n*Overthrow of the Somoza family dictatorship\n*Rise to power of the National Opposition Union \n*Start of the U.S. backed [[Contras|Contra War]]\n|-\n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| [[Mexican Dirty War|Dirty War]]<br/>(1968&ndash;1982)\n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| {{flag|Mexico|size=23px}}<br/>{{flag|United States|size=23px}}<br/>Special \"White Brigade\" and [[Death squad|other death squads]]\n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| [[Left-wing]] groups:\n* [[Party of the Poor (Mexico)|Party of the Poor]]\n* [[Liga Comunista 23 de Septiembre]]\n* {{flagicon image|Flag of the EZLN.svg|size=23px}} [[Zapatista Army of National Liberation|EZLN]]\n* {{flagicon image|Mx-epr.gif}} [[Popular Revolutionary Army|EPR]]\n*Various social and armed movements in the country\n|style=\"background:#D0FFD0\"| '''Victory'''\n* Continued rule of the [[Institutional Revolutionary Party]]\n* Most leftist guerrilla groups disbanded\n|-\n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| [[Zapatista uprising|Zapatista Uprising]]<br/>(1994)\n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| {{flag|Mexico|size=23px}}                      {{Flagicon|United States}} [[United States]]\n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| {{flagicon image|Flag of the EZLN.svg|size=23px}} [[Zapatista A