oatia|size=23px|name=Croatia}}<br />{{flag|Slovak Republic (1939\u20131945)|size=23px|name=Slovakia}}<br />{{flag|State of Burma|1943|size=23px}}\n |style=\"background:#D0FFD0\"| '''Victory'''\n* Collapse of the [[Nazi Germany|Third Reich]]\n* Fall of [[Empire of Japan|Japanese]] and [[Italian Empire]]s\n* Creation of the [[United Nations]]\n* Emergence of the [[United States]] and the [[Soviet Union]] as [[superpower]]s\n* Beginning of the [[Cold War]]\n|-\n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| [[Mexico\u2013Guatemala conflict|Mexico\u2013Guatemala Conflict]]<br/>(1958&ndash;1959)\n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| {{flag|Mexico|1934|size=23px}} \n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| {{flag|Guatemala|size=23px}}\n|style=\"background:#E0D0FF\"| '''Ceasefire'''\n* Mexican retaliation halted by newly elected president [[Adolfo L\u00f3pez Mateos]]\n* Diplomatic relations between the two nations are frozen for several months\n* South American meditation helps to prevent escalation\n|-\n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| [[Nicaraguan Revolution]]<br/>(1962&ndash;1990)\n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| {{flagicon image|Flag of the FSLN.png|size=22px}} [[Sandinista National Liberation Front|FSLN]]<br/>{{flag|Soviet Union|1955|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Libya|1977|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Cuba|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Bulgaria|1971|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Romania|1952|size=22px}}<br/>{{flagicon|Czech Republic|size=22px}} [[Czechoslovakia]]<br/>{{flag|Poland|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Mexico|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|East Germany|1959|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Chile|size=22px}} (until 1973)\n|style=\"background:#efefef\"| {{flagicon|Nicaragua|size=22px}} [[Somoza family|Somoza Dynasty]]<br/>{{flag|United States|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Israel|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Saudi Arabia|1938|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Honduras|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Chile|size=22px}} (since 1973)<br/>{{flag|Brazil|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Paraguay|1954|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Argentina|size=22px}}<br/>{{flag|Panama|size=22px}}<br/>{{flagicon|Germany